40
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:15,000
<font color="#ffffff">med mig.</font>

41
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,120
<font color="#ffffff">Men vad händer egentligen?</font>

42
00:02:16,479 --> 00:02:18,080
<font color="#ffffff">Den tid jag var
